	- **read data from files in a directory: jobs**
		- background
			- these are .md files, each file contains layout for a job advertisement
			- our module component creates for each job an object in an array called jobs
				- each object contains HTML that was parsed from the markdown content in the file
			- to add a new object, one simply has to add a new .md file
		- download [this repository](https://github.com/edwardtanguay/howto-node-express-server-side-mvc)
