		- set up build process to transpile TypeScript to JavaScript
			- since TypeScript compiles to JavaScript at build time, **Heroku is going to execute JavaScript, not TypeScript**
			- therefore we need to prepare our site to be able to execute our the TypeScript-transpiled JavaScript
			- in **package.json**, create a build script to execute the TypeScript compiler (tsc)
