				- note the absense of TypeScript code in the generated JavaScript:
					- our TypeScript interface is gone
					- all our TypeScript type references are gone
			- actually this generated JavaScript belongs in a "build" directory, not in our "src" file
				- delete the file `src/server.js`
				- in **tsconfig.json** add the following setting:
					-------------------------------------
					"outDir": "build"
