- **what we will build**
	- a multi-page React site in which we create custom hooks which are reused
	- we will use React Router to create a minimalistic menu of pages
	- on each page we will demonstrate who we use the custom hooks we make
- **what are custom hooks?**
	- hooks are functions that let you hook into React state so that when something changes you do something specific and useful
	- custom hooks enable you to identify repetitive code and condense it into a function that can be called from mulitple places in code
		- the function generally returns an object or array of numerous values, some of which are functions
